## 📌 About Project
**Luxentra** is a modern hotel reservation website UI/UX design focused on delivering a smooth and premium booking experience.  
The design emphasizes luxury aesthetics, easy navigation, and a seamless user journey from browsing hotels to completing reservations.

---

## ✨ Features
- 🏨 Elegant Home Page Design  
- 🔍 Smart Hotel Search & Listing UI  
- 📅 Smooth Booking Flow  
- 💳 Checkout & Reservation Concept  
- 📱 Responsive UI Design  

